org.apache.poi.ss.formula.functions

Class Subtotal

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ss.formula.functions.Subtotal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Function 

    public class Subtotal
extends java.lang.Object
implements Function
    Implementation for the Excel function SUBTOTAL

    Syntax :
    SUBTOTAL ( functionCode, ref1, ref2 ... )

    functionCode (1-11) Selects the underlying aggregate function to be used (see table below)
    ref1, ref2 ... Arguments to be passed to the underlying aggregate function

    functionCode Aggregate Function
    1 AVERAGE
    2 COUNT
    3 COUNTA
    4 MAX
    5 MIN
    6 PRODUCT
    7 STDEV
    8 STDEVP *
    9 SUM
    10 VAR *
    11 VARP *
    101 AVERAGE
    102 COUNT
    103 COUNTA
    104 MAX
    105 MIN
    106 PRODUCT
    107 STDEV
    108 STDEVP *
    109 SUM
    110 VAR *
    111 VARP *

    * Not implemented in POI yet. Functions 101-111 are the same as functions 1-11 but with the option 'ignore hidden values'.

    (Excel函数SUBTOAL的实现：SUBTOAL（functionCode，ref 1，ref 2.）functionCode（1-11）指定要使用的基础聚合函数（请参阅下表）ref 1、ref 2.要传递给基础聚合函数函数的参数代码聚合函数1平均值2 RST 3 COUNTA 4 MAX 5 Min 6 GROUP 7 STdev 8 STDEVP * 9 SUM 10 VAR * 11 VAR * 101平均值102 RST 103 COUNTA 104 MAX 105 Min 106 GROUP 107 STdev 108 STDEVP * 109 SUM 110 VAR * 111 VAR * 111 VAR ** 尚未在兴趣点中实施。函数101- 1 - 11与函数1-11相同，但具有“忽略隐藏值”选项。)
    Author:
    Paul Tomlin < pault at bulk sms dot com >

      • evaluate

        public ValueEval evaluate(ValueEval[] args,
                          int srcRowIndex,
                          int srcColumnIndex)
        Specified by:
        evaluate in interface Function(在接口函数中求值)
        Parameters:
        args - the evaluated function arguments. Empty values are represented with BlankEval or MissingArgEval, never null.(args -已计算的函数参数。空值用BlankEval或MissingArgEval表示，绝不能为空。)
        srcRowIndex - row index of the cell containing the formula under evaluation(srcRowIndex -包含正在评估的公式的单元格的行索引)
        srcColumnIndex - column index of the cell containing the formula under evaluation(srcColumnIndex -包含正在评估的公式的单元格的列索引)
        Returns:
        The evaluated result, possibly an ErrorEval, never null. Note - Excel uses the error code #NUM! instead of IEEE NaN, so when numeric functions evaluate to Double.NaN be sure to translate the result to ErrorEval.NUM_ERROR.(评估的结果（可能是errorEval）永远不会为空。注意- Excel使用错误代码#NUM！而不是IEEE NaN，因此当数字函数的计算结果为Double.NaN时，请确保将结果翻译为WRRFAL.NUM_BER。)
